X = torch.tensor(1., requires_grad=True)
W = torch.tensor(2., requires_grad=True)
B = torch.tensor(3., requires_grad=True)


Y = W * X + B    # y = 2 * x + 3

# Compute gradients.
Y.backward()

# Print out the gradients.
print(X.grad)    # x.grad = 2 
print(W.grad)    # w.grad = 1 
print(B.grad)    # b.grad = 1
